{"tid":1379593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開)【入黎簽野】叫美國唔好再供應裝備俾警察","createTime":"2019-07-28T21:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T20:00:38.000Z","uid":232863,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c156c9ffa0fd0cfabf93a4e4f6e9fc790bc34ddd","tid":1379593,"uid":232863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:23:25.000Z","msg":"上個post俾個巴打用bot 10秒自動推一次，一定會推到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以重新開多一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyyyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=b51e1bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses</a><br />\n<strong><em>Petition calling for the suspension of crowd control equipment exports to Hong Kong, prevent human rights abuses</em></strong><br />\n<br />\nIn recent years, Hong Kong police have purchased more aggressive crowd control equipment from foreign countries. The US is one of the major suppliers for items including pepperball guns, bean bag rounds, rubber rounds and pepper spray. These weapons are repeatedly misused to suppress protestors and even journalists in HK's recent anti-extradition protests, such as shooting protestors' heads, using pepper spray at close range, and unleashing tear gas directly at unarmed protestors. Such violations of human rights should be condemned and sanctioned, otherwise, it would only encourage further abuse of excessive force.<br />\n<br />\nWe, therefore, strongly urge the US government to suspend any export application of crowd control equipment to Hong Kong to prevent further brutality against Hong Kongers.<br />\n<strong><br />\nNeeds 93,366 signatures by <span style=\"color: red;\">August 4, 2019</span> to get a response from the White House</strong><br />\n<br />\n<code>8月5齊罷工</code>"},{"pid":"c7ea04799b551b6f69df0a631d3a8170316ffbad","tid":1379593,"uid":35084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:25:55.000Z","msg":"你開po 要吊埋 連登姐姐惡意推po先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8733e5bc54e2c2ee64249c6f69bb77afe2c54efc","tid":1379593,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:25:57.000Z","msg":"其實美國一邊話香港政府應該聽下市民聲音<br />\n一邊賣d武器、裝備比香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申已簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e78b01b41bf92528f9c4e349509057734a22df","tid":1379593,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:26:35.000Z","msg":"推po"},{"pid":"65b19d64aae57a86c06969c75b1e2c283a982240","tid":1379593,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:29:49.000Z","msg":"Push push 睇我搶唔搶到舊po 1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21ffaa050a1dde51f1cc2bc0e4ef4637c658bc4","tid":1379593,"uid":232863,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7ea04799b551b6f69df0a631d3a8170316ffbad","tid":1379593,"uid":35084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:25:55.000Z","msg":"你開po 要吊埋 連登姐姐惡意推po先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:29:51.000Z","msg":"依家屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連登姐姐</strong>我屌你老母啊,唔好開完個推po bot就走去訓喇,凌晨洗爆個po有撚用咩</span></span><br />\n屌完,希望連登姐姐下次唔好咁傻豬豬開完個bot走去訓<img src=\"/ass